            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Quen ilhuichihuah altepetzitzin, quence quemman pixcah zo quemman ce acahya iilhui, nouhquiya ce tlamantli paquiliztli tlen ce tlaneltoquilli huan campa quimanextia ce tlamantli tlamahuizolli.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
